acb505c08afcfb94903988c20a","tid":1538082,"uid":227628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:10:01.000Z","msg":"改做四大訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0a6ce5fcba2f147955a8547f975af4042c88c69","tid":1538082,"uid":227628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aba66b9cf578d7ce5f35ff27701892c0db25ebae","tid":1538082,"uid":121869,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:26:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mS3qqGn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmS3qqGn.jpg&h=e0db4b33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我地不如整理下殉國手足，然後一世都記住佢地，好嗎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532408\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532408</a><br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n民族自強 港人自救<br />\n沒有暴徒 只有暴政<br />\n五大訴求<span style=\"color: red;\"> 缺一不可</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:10:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e51b1926a39812f9f16117deb15552678f51ef57","tid":1538082,"uid":98002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:11:08.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\nFIVE DEMANDS - NOT ONE LESS</span></span></span></strong></div>"},{"pid":"0ac1a26b49a410215ab035974a30a0cfc0ec0910","tid":1538082,"uid":72800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:11:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xcgb58P.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxcgb58P.gif&h=4c045c7d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ep8qq8P.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEp8qq8P.gif&h=b74f62eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong><em><div style=\"text-align: center;\">毋忘七烈 千一義 四眼 三十骨折 手腳筋<br />\n721元朗 811警暴 831車廂 雙肺 一裙<br />\n無數屈辱私刑 重傷昏迷<br />\n<br />\n撤回 定性 釋士 究警 普選</div></em></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港共殺人政權企圖以<strong>錄音、撤回、學季開始</strong><br />\n轉移<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">太子地鐵傷亡、<br />\n六警壓脊椎休克 至今嚴重昏迷、<br />\n新屋嶺、民主人權法案</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>核彈</strong></span><span style=\"color: red;\">事件焦點<br />\n醒呀大家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">政府帶緊風向</span><br />\n背後繼續大清算 入獄 利刑 一年後被失蹤</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">暗黑兵法劇本 出沒注意：\n\n沒收gear 未來兩星期大量武警喬裝示威者 嫁禍衝擊\n內部分化示威者、\n酷刑凌虐威嚇被捕人士、\n邊緣打壓香港 渲染港獨 阻抗爭之風蔓延內陸、\n假新聞、擺拍、編輯、洗腦文宣製造風向 污名化運動、\n暴力鎮壓 拘捕 扣留 私刑 企圖瓦解前線、\n文宣 抹黑 嫁禍 插贜 示威者、\n暗殺 第一滴血 企圖逆轉民意 國際譴責、\n市民絕望噤聲 憤怒冷卻、\n中立派 賺錢派 政治疲勞、\n鼓吹經濟下滑風向 富豪商家屈服 加速瓦解、\n學季始開，拖延 分散 擊破、\n白色恐怖、清除異己、染紅香港\n\n拖字訣 雨傘結局 ⋯</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n袋住先 放風降溫<br />\n大追捕 清算 正式開始<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>這不只是反修例活動<br />\n這是屬於香港人的<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">時代革命</span></strong></span></div>"},{"pid":"6b056e3a9f88dde117b328c7044104ac1b87f32c","tid":1538082,"uid":72800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:12:21.000Z","msg":"無勝利過<br />\n邏輯錯曬"}]}